data.text:
Shakira's hips don't lie: The Colombian singer has given birth!

Shakira and her beau, Spanish National soccer player Gerard Piqué, welcomed their first child Tuesday, according to People en Espanol. Their newborn son, who reportedly was born in Barcelona, is named Milan.

Check out the first photo of Shakira's unborn baby

Earlier in the day, Shakira reached out to her fans for their well wishes. "I'd like to ask you all to accompany me in your prayers on this very important day of my life," she tweeted.

Shakira, 35, announced she was expecting in September after going public with Piqué in March 2011. She will next be seen stateside in March as a new coach on The Voice.
